snippet.title: Pre-Order Trailer | Marathon
snippet.description:
Marathon releases March 5, 2026. 

Secrets. Buried and rotting. With the UESC holding the shovel.  
That's where you come in, Runner.

Scavenge the lost colony of Tau Ceti IV in the survival extraction FPS from the creators of Halo and Destiny.

Pre-order Marathon now: 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3065800/Marathon/
PlayStation 5: https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/marathon/
Xbox Series X|S: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p8mgmxndv9b

Learn more: https://bung.ie/4rl5QfF

Follow Marathon:
TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@marathonthegame
Instagram: https://instagram.com/marathonthegame
Twitter: https://x.com/marathonthegame
Bluesky: https://bsky.app/profile/marathonthegame.bungie.net
Discord: https://discord.gg/marathonthegame

Infil into the dark sci-fi world of Tau Ceti IV: A derelict colony rife with rival Runners, hostile UESC security forces, and unpredictable environments. Play with your crew, as a solo Runner, or form uneasy alliances with proximity chat. Scavenge, buildcraft, and take on greater challenges–culminating with the derelict Marathon ship hanging above.

snippet.title: How Minecraft Manhunt is Made...
snippet.description:
How Minecraft Manhunt is Made... FIVE HUNTERS REVIVAL SOON!

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

A lot of people ask about this, so I decided to make an entire video on it now that Minecraft Manhunt is coming back!

If you want to make your own #minecraftmanhunt videos, I would recommend you follow a similar process!

This video doesn't talk at all about the practice beforehand, or the editing afterwards, which both contribute massively to the quality of the videos. This just talks about the RULES of Manhunt and how the recording process works.

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - Final Trailer "Rise Of Doom" | Chris Hemsworth, Chris Evans | 2026
snippet.description:
#thor  #marvelstudios #chrishemsworth 

Watch the 'FAN (CONCEPT) Trailer Concept' For Marvel Studios' Avengers: Doomsday (2026) (More Info About This Video Down Below!)

▶️ Watch More Concept Trailers:

Harry Potter and the Cursed Child Trailer - https://youtu.be/OnwogtoNJSA 👈

Frozen: Live Action Movie Trailer -  https://youtu.be/5FlLO5EpNic 👈

Pirates of the Caribbean 6 Trailer - https://youtu.be/uncc9uN0bbI👈

"Avengers: Doomsday" is the highly anticipated fifth installment in the core Avengers series, slated for release on December 18, 2026, marking a major event in Phase Six of the Marvel Cinematic Universe. Directed by the Russo Brothers—Anthony and Joe Russo—the film reunites many beloved heroes and introduces new alliances. As the MCU expands its multiverse saga, this crossover brings together iconic teams such as the Avengers, Fantastic Four, X-Men, Wakandans, and the New Avengers to confront the formidable villain Doctor Doom, portrayed in a stunning twist by Robert Downey Jr.

The ensemble cast features returning favorites such as Chris Hemsworth (Thor), Anthony Mackie (Captain America), Paul Rudd (Ant-Man), Letitia Wright (Shuri), Tom Hiddleston (Loki), Florence Pugh (Yelena), and many more. Among its most notable reunions are X-Men legends Patrick Stewart (Professor X), Ian McKellen (Magneto), Alan Cumming (Nightcrawler), Rebecca Romijn (Mystique) and James Marsden (Cyclops). The Fantastic Four join the fray with Vanessa Kirby as Sue Storm and Pedro Pascal as Reed Richards. The film's story picks up 14 months after Thunderbolts (2025), as multiple superhero teams unite against Doctor Doom's machinations in an epic multiverse showdown.

Alan Silvestri, acclaimed composer of previous MCU hits, returns to score Avengers: Doomsday, promising a powerful musical backbone. The screenplay is crafted by Michael Waldron and Stephen McFeely, combining fresh narrative perspectives with seasoned MCU storytelling. Filming commenced in April 2025 at Pinewood Studios in England and will span approximately six months, underscoring Marvel's ambitious scale and logistical coordination. With a release date firmly set for December 18, 2026, and a sequel (Avengers: Secret Wars) slated for December 17, 2027, Doomsday is positioned as a pivotal chapter in the concluding arc of the MCU’s Multiverse Saga.

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @GalacticTrailerOfficial 
Please subscribe:
✅YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/GalacticTrailerOfficial
✅Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/darthvideos/
✅Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@darthtrailer
✅ Twitter: https://twitter.com/Darth_Trailer
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Software I use: Adobe Premiere, After Effects, Photoshop, Adobe Audition, Unreal Engine 5.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

◁ On our channel, we create trailer mashups ▷ Trailer mashups, also known as recut trailers, are crafted by gathering various film footage from one or more movies and re-editing them to form a brand-new trailer. These mashups often depict a movie that doesn’t exist or shift the genre of an existing film. As derivative works defined under the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. § 101, they may be protected from copyright claims under the fair use doctrine.

Trailer mashups are not just a form of user-generated digital creativity but also a unique way to build excitement for upcoming releases, complementing official movie trailers. While traditional trailers tease the plot and generate hype, fan-made mashups let the audience put their own cinematic twist on existing footage. This creative freedom can spotlight a particular actor, emphasize a specific storyline, or even transform the film’s genre entirely.

This video is a parody. Due to its derivative and transformative nature, it is protected under Fair Use.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thank You So Much For Watching!
May the force be with us, Always!

snippet.title: "Piece of Denmark" - Marsh Family parody of "Piece of My Heart" by Erma Franklin on Greenland/Trump
snippet.description:
This is a hasty cover of Erma Franklin's 1967 belter, written by Jerry Ragovoy and Bert Berns, that is one of our favourite soul tracks, and only lost out to a Grammy to her younger sister Aretha in 1969 ("Chain of Fools"). It had a resurgence in Europe in the early 90s after the end of the Cold War thanks to a Levi jeans advert, and its highest chart position for the re-release was number 5 ... in Denmark.

Our treatment pays tribute to the Danes (who suffered proportionally among the highest casualties in wars supporting the USA after its triggering the collective security clauses of NATO in places like Iraq and Afghanistan), and who are being shaken down at the moment by the likes of Trump, Vance, and Miller in their bid to bully Europe to agree to the annexation of autonomous Greenlanders. You probably don't need a link to make sense of this, as it's all over the news, but in case: https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c4g5345ylk0o. 

There are (again) some rude words in our parody lyrics, for which apologies, as we continue to respond to stress by swearing, which can actually be very cathartic and good for you, as long as you can stop it spreading to your kids: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypoalgesic_effect_of_swearing. 

___________________________ 

Support us here: 
- PayPal to leave us a tip jar: https://paypal.me/marshfamilysongs 
- Patreon for ongoing support & bonuses: https://www.patreon.com/marshfamilysongs 
- Crowdfunder for debut album out in 2026: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/marshfamily/the-marsh-family-debut-album-campaign 

Find our other channels here: https://linktr.ee/marshfamilysongs 

Follow us here: 
- https://www.marshfamilysongs.com 
- https://www.facebook.com/MarshFamilySongs/ 
- https://www.instagram.com/marshfamilysongs/ 
- https://twitter.com/MarshSongs 
- https://www.threads.net/@marshfamilysongs 
- https://www.tiktok.com/@marshfamilysongs 
- https://bsky.app/profile/marshfamilysongs.bsky.social 
- https://open.spotify.com/artist/6AYmbCwi92V29y69lkRkRa 

___________________________

LYRICS

Didn’t Danes show their steel when you fought the Taliban?
Didn’t they give you everything – when you reckon per capita?
But, with all the stuff they gave ya, it’s never enough …
The guy-toddler bone-spur baby’s grabbing Greenland in a huff!

So, come on … come on … come on … come on …
It’s a mother-f&*king piece of Denmark, he’s crazy! (BREAK IT!)
Break another old alliance apart, for money?! (HAVE A…)
Have another little change of the heart, now, maybe?!
You know he’s lost it if he’s threatening Nuuk!

He’s flouting the peace (DOIN’ NO GOOD)
Congress knows deep down in their heart, that it ain’t right
But oh, they’ll never, never stop him till defeat’s in sight, oh …
He tells us all, there’ll be tariffs and pain
But when it’s NATO up in arms, he’s selling out friends:

So Donald … Donald … Donald … Donald: quit it
It’s a mother-f&*king piece of Denmark, he’s crazy! (QUIT IT!)
Taking ownership is not on the cards – they’re all free! (RIP IT!)
Rip another little treaty apart, trivially?
You know it’s rotten but it makes him feel good

It’s a mother-f&*king piece of Denmark, he’s crazy!
Get some other person playing the part, now maybe?
Have the 25th Amendment kickstart, now maybe?!

…
